You have 2 choices here. You can pass and hope the opponents bid so that partner does not have to play 1N with 14-16 HCP between the 2 hands. Or you can bid 2@S (club transfer), intending to play 3@C. I recommend you bid 2@S, but the choice is not clear cut.
